{"tid":2110903,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[SellHK] 御海灣(灣灣)首推88伙　平均呎價17,377元　入場費468萬元起","createTime":"2020-07-16T08:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T01:41:07.000Z","uid":75355,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adc6c74ec199d3798d6d72b33fbc5b391163f94a","tid":2110903,"uid":75355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"國家安全  龍市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情雖未過去，但無阻發展商開盤部署。新鴻基地產(00016)旗下屯門御海灣，今日(16日)公布首批單位開價。新地代理業務部總經理張卓秀敏稱，首張價單推出88伙，實用面積261至437方呎，扣除最高22%折扣優惠後，折實售價468.88萬至714.32萬元，呎價14,992至19,592元，折實平均呎價17,377元。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，整批單位折實平均呎價17,377元，與同系區內御半山目前售價相若，開價屬貼市價，本周六(18日)起開放示範單位及收票，最快下周開售。<br />\n資料顯示，同系區內御半山II期，於2019年6月公布開價，首批單位折實平均呎價15,166元。"},{"pid":"68f1e2b04568126738862ab662cca6aa3645d4d3","tid":2110903,"uid":75355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">未來</span>西鐵沿線17K 搶呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc7007e1c4818190b260fd4110033495dca9cd5","tid":2110903,"uid":321157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"抵到爛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9e53c5fa548e62ead7a187398da28e9c913407","tid":2110903,"uid":94801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"好抵 22k 先叫貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e9f2730c42114032f9f99a2d8897ac6739950ed","tid":2110903,"uid":154433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:24:30.000Z","msg":"抵呀 用市區價住灣灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4be05497026123925c45bc9d8ed7d927aff1464","tid":2110903,"uid":221395,"like":0,"dislike